ona Stoyanova updated list of languages\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-20\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-12-18\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2025-12-10\" who=\"#DD\">Dmitry Dundua's lemmatizations were added from source CoNLL-U files\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2025-12-10\" who=\"#RC\">Robert Crellin integrated lemmatizations into EpiDoc using PyEpiDoc and associated scripts\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2025-12-16\" who=\"#ZL\">tagged names and persons\u003C/change>\n            \u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic001206_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001206.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n        \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>\u003Cw n=\"5\">Δίοκλε\u003C/w>\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003Cw n=\"10\">χαῖρε\u003C/w>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"simple-lemmatized\" resp=\"#DD #RC\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Cw n=\"5\" lemma=\"Διοκλῆς\">Δίοκλε\u003C/w>\n                    \u003Cw n=\"10\" lemma=\"χαίρω\">χαῖρε\u003C/w>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text as per IG and IGMusPal\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>Diokles, farewell!\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>The name is in the vocative form of \u003Cref target=\"http://clas-lgpn2.classics.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/lgpn_search.cgi?name=%CE%94%CE%B9%CE%BF%CE%BA%CE%BB%E1%BF%86%CF%82\">Διοκλῆς\u003C/ref>, a common name, widely attested in Sicily.  The suggestion of Manni Piraino that it derives from a form Δίοκλος (suggested to be attested by \u003Cref target=\"http://data.perseus.org/citations/urn:cts:latinLit:phi0474.phi005.perseus-eng1:2.5.16\">Cic. Verr. 2.5.16\u003C/ref>:  de Apollonio, Diocli1 filio, Panhormitano, cui gemino cognomen est) seems implausible. The form Δίοκλος (LGPN V3B: 37428) is only attested once, and the form in the Verrines is surely a latinisation of convenience. There is no obvious reason to date this to the early imperial period (as Manni Piraino does); the letter forms - as well as the contextual evidence of the Hellenistic necropolis at Abakainon - suggest a Hellenistic date.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\">382a\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q2SBPG9F\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IGMusPalermo\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manni Piraino\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1973\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>125\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F66S4X3M\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000531\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000531\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"NSA\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Salinas\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Ctitle>NSA\u003C/title>\n                        \u003Cdate>1886\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>464 no.d\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4MCP2PVV\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"SGDI\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Hoffmann\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1904\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>5208a\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/DQDPC573\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Sofia\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2015\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>108 and fig.112\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/9QTE4E3Z\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001575\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001575\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\n                    \u003Cbibl/>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
